{"version": "https://jsonfeed.org/version/1.1", "title": "\u57fa\u5ca9\u6587\u6863", "home_page_url": "https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/", "feed_url": "https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/feed_json_updated.json", "description": "Minecraft\u57fa\u5ca9\u7248\u5f00\u53d1\u6587\u6863", "icon": null, "authors": [], "language": "zh", "items": [{"id": "https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/blog/category/%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF/", "url": "https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/blog/category/%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF/", "title": "\u6280\u672f", "content_html": "<h1>\u6280\u672f</h1>", "image": "https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/assets/images/social/blog/category/\u6280\u672f.png", "date_modified": "2026-05-24T14:15:43.822168+00:00", "date_published": "2026-05-24T14:15:43.822162+00:00", "authors": [], "tags": null}, {"id": "https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/blog/archive/2024/", "url": "https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/blog/archive/2024/", "title": "2024", "content_html": "<h1>2024</h1>", "image": "https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/assets/images/social/blog/archive/2024.png", "date_modified": "2026-05-24T14:15:43.644815+00:00", "date_published": "2026-05-24T14:15:43.644808+00:00", "authors": [], "tags": null}, {"id": "https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/docs/server/plugin/", "url": "https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/docs/server/plugin/", "title": "\u63d2\u4ef6", "content_html": "<h1>\u63d2\u4ef6</h1>\n<p><strong>\u63d2\u4ef6\uff08Plugin\uff09</strong>\u662fMinecraft\u57fa\u5ca9\u7248\u670d\u52a1\u7aef\u4e2d\u7528\u4e8e\u6269\u5c55\u548c\u4fee\u6539\u670d\u52a1\u7aef\u884c\u4e3a\u7684\u7a0b\u5e8f\u3002\u4e0e\u9644\u52a0\u5305\u4e0d\u540c\uff0c\u63d2\u4ef6\u8fd0\u884c\u5728\u670d\u52a1\u7aef\u8f6f\u4ef6\u4e0a\uff0c\u901a\u8fc7\u8c03\u7528\u670d\u52a1\u7aef\u63d0\u4f9b\u7684API\u6765\u5b9e\u73b0\u6e38\u620f\u903b\u8f91\u7684\u4fee\u6539\u548c\u6269\u5c55\u3002</p>\n<h2>\u6982\u8ff0</h2>\n<p>\u57fa\u5ca9\u7248\u7684\u9644\u52a0\u5305\u7cfb\u7edf\u63d0\u4f9b\u4e86\u6570\u636e\u9a71\u52a8\u548c\u811a\u672cAPI\u4e24\u79cd\u5b98\u65b9\u6269\u5c55\u673a\u5236\uff0c\u4f46\u5b83\u4eec\u7684\u80fd\u529b\u53d7\u9650\u4e8e\u5b98\u65b9\u516c\u5f00\u7684\u63a5\u53e3\u8303\u56f4...</p>", "image": "https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/assets/images/social/docs/server/plugin.png", "date_modified": "2026-05-24T14:01:50+00:00", "date_published": "2026-04-07T14:42:50+00:00", "authors": [], "tags": null}, {"id": "https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/guides/servers/serenity/", "url": "https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/guides/servers/serenity/", "title": "SerenityJS\u5165\u95e8", "content_html": "<h1>SerenityJS\u5165\u95e8</h1>\n<p>SerenityJS\u662f\u4e00\u4e2a\u9762\u5411Node.js\u751f\u6001\u7684Minecraft\u57fa\u5ca9\u7248\u81ea\u5b9e\u73b0\u670d\u52a1\u7aef\u3002\u5b83\u9002\u5408\u60f3\u7528TypeScript\u6216JavaScript\u7ec4\u7ec7\u670d\u52a1\u5668\u903b\u8f91\uff0c\u6216\u8005\u60f3\u628a\u57fa\u5ca9\u7248\u670d\u52a1\u5668\u5d4c\u5165\u5230\u666e\u901aNode.js/Bun\u9879\u76ee\u4e2d\u7684\u5f00\u53d1\u8005\u3002\u60f3\u5148\u4e86\u89e3\u5b9a\u4f4d\u548c\u8fb9\u754c\uff0c\u53ef\u4ee5\u9605\u8bfb[SerenityJS](.....</p>", "image": "https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/assets/images/social/guides/servers/serenity.png", "date_modified": "2026-05-24T14:01:50+00:00", "date_published": "2026-05-23T15:16:46+00:00", "authors": [], "tags": null}, {"id": "https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/docs/server/allay/", "url": "https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/docs/server/allay/", "title": "Allay", "content_html": "<h1>Allay</h1>\n<p><strong>Allay</strong>\u662f\u9762\u5411Minecraft\u57fa\u5ca9\u7248\u7684\u7b2c\u4e09\u65b9\u81ea\u5b9e\u73b0\u670d\u52a1\u7aef\u8f6f\u4ef6\u3002\u5b83\u4f7f\u7528Java21\u8fd0\u884c\uff0c\u4ece\u7f51\u7edc\u534f\u8bae\u3001\u4e16\u754c\u7ba1\u7406\u3001\u5b9e\u4f53\u7cfb\u7edf\u3001\u65b9\u5757\u7cfb\u7edf\u3001\u7269\u54c1\u7cfb